QuestData.Title: Adventurers Wanted: Maraudon
QuestData.Description: The Warchief has requested that any able-bodied adventurer head to Maraudon, in western Desolace, immediately!$B$BHealing Maraudon from its current corruption would great help the entirety of Desolace! If you so choose, head to Maraudon and speak with Zaetar's Spirit, he will guide you.
